No. 10-446. Charles Kerchner, Jr., et al., Petitioners v. Barack H. Obama, President of the United States, et al. 562 U.S. 1082, 131 S. Ct. 663, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 9199.

178 L. Ed. 2d 513,

November 29, 2010.

Motion of Western Center for Journalism for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.

Same case below, 612 F.3d 204.
